OL,7,FITV West Country's Robert Murphy
OL,8,Fspeaks to residents and staff ahead of
OL,9,Fthe closures
OL,11,FA man has expressed his shock and
OL,12,Fconcern at how plans to close his
OL,13,Fwife's care home in Somerset will
OL,14,Fimpact her dementia.
OL,16,FGill Baker is 83-years-old and lives
OL,17,Fat Critchill Court in Frome and has
OL,18,Ffound the site, run by Somerset Care,
OL,19,Fhas proved a lifeline after her
OL,20,Fhusband Clive struggles to cope.
