OL,7,FBut Gill and residents both at
OL,8,FCritchill Court and Sunnymeade in
OL,9,FChard were told that , as the operator
OL,10,Fcan no longer afford to keep them
OL,11,Frunning.
OL,13,FClive said: "Earlier this week, they
OL,14,Finvited our daughter to a meeting -
OL,15,Fnot me - and they just abruptly said,
OL,16,F'this is just to let you know that we
OL,17,Fwill be closing at the end of April.'"
OL,19,FClive said the announcement left him
OL,20,Fin "shock".
