OL,7,F"I couldn't really believe it", he
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FThe announcement means all residents
OL,11,Fwill have to find alternative places
OL,12,Fto live - and as some have complex and
OL,13,Fprofound needs, this could prove
OL,14,Fdifficult.
OL,16,F"We've obviously got to plan forward
OL,17,Fand get on the case", Clive said.
