OL,7,F"Indeed, my daughter has been hunting
OL,8,Fthis morning for another home in the
OL,9,Farea and we believe she has found
OL,10,Fone," he added.
OL,12,FUNISON: 'Redundancy may mean some
OL,13,Fstaff lose their ability to stay in
OL,14,Fthe UK'
OL,16,FAs well as all the residents having to
OL,17,Ffind new homes, staff at both sites
OL,18,Fhave been told they face redundancy.
