OL,7,FThe workers' union, UNISON, has said
OL,8,Fit is concerned for many of their
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FTom Kennedy-Hughes, an area organiser
OL,12,Ffor the union, said: "There are staff
OL,13,Fthat are on sponsorship and they are
OL,14,Fvery concerned, because the risk of
OL,15,Fthe redundancy to them could means not
OL,16,Fjust losing their jobs but not being
OL,17,Fable to stay in the UK.
