OL,7,F"So, there is a real concern to that
OL,8,Fgroup of workers and we want to
OL,9,Freassure them that we will be working
OL,10,Fwith their employer to find solutions."
OL,12,FSomerset Care told ITV News that the
OL,13,Fcentres met care requirements when
OL,14,Fthey were built in the 1970s and 80s,
OL,15,Fbut that it has found they are unable
OL,16,Fto keep pace with modern demands.
