OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,8,Fnot-for-profit company, said:
OL,9,F"Somerset Care is not immune to the
OL,10,Ffinancial challenges faced by the
OL,11,Fwider care sector.
OL,13,F"The much-publicised chronic
OL,14,Funderfunding of the adult social care
OL,15,Fsector on a national level, along with
OL,16,Fthe financial emergency declared by
OL,17,FSomerset Council, mean that the Local
OL,18,FAuthority care fees we receive do not
OL,19,Fmeet the real cost of delivering the
OL,20,Fcare which we are being asked to
OL,21,Fprovide."
