OL,7,FAddressing the closures, Somerset
OL,8,FCouncil told ITV News that "the safety
OL,9,Fand wellbeing of residents is its top
OL,10,Fpriority", and that their adult social
OL,11,Fcare team have "already been on site
OL,12,Fto support residents and their
OL,13,Ffamilies during this difficult time".
